---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="Colt Camron Lien" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Colt Camron Lien</h1>
      <h3>Conductor | Educator | Polymath</h3>
      <a href="/research" class="btn">Peruse Scholarly Work</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="manifesto">
    <h2>Who am I? What am I? Even I don't know.</h2>
    <p>
      As I step into continually more adventures, I find it increasingly difficult to
      place myself into a single category or field of study. So welcome to the mess. 
      Here you'll find my extended biography, contact information, and a collection of 
      my various work. Sometimes it's music, sometimes it's physics. I guess that's okay?
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr style="border-color: var(--card-bg); margin: 3rem 0;" />

  <section class="featured-work">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Current Focus</h2>
    
    <div class="card-grid">
      <a href="/research" class="focus-card">
        <h3>Theoretical Frameworks & Systems</h3>
        <p>Active research modeling the universe as a continuous superfluid, alongside bare-metal Rust development for TorusOS.</p>
        <span class="card-link">View Manuscripts &rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/music" class="focus-card">
        <h3>Choral Direction & Literature</h3>
        <p>Designing authentic, high-level musical experiences that explore diverse cultures and convey compelling human messages.</p>
        <span class="card-link">View Music &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .card-grid {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .card-grid {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }

  .focus-card {
    flex: 1;
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-color);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .focus-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .focus-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .focus-card p {
    flex-grow: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .card-link {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }
</style>